   "item": "H.3",
   "desc": "Price Transparency \u2014 CDM Layer (Phase 1 Complete) + MRF Compliance (Phase 2)",
   "owner": "Compliance / Revenue Cycle",
   "secondary": "Required \u2014 Week 2",
   "scope": "(1) Is the hospital\u2019s machine-readable file (MRF) currently posted publicly? Please provide the URL. (2) Does the consumer-friendly shoppable services display include at least 300 services (70 CMS-specified + 230 hospital-selected)? (3) For the 17 CMS-specified services not found in the outpatient CDM: confirm for each whether the service is offered and if so whether it is captured elsewhere. (4) Price 93000 (ECG routine) \u2014 currently $0 in CDM; assign current price immediately. NOTE: This engagement validates CDM presence only \u2014 MRF JSON schema compliance, five standard charge types, and consumer display are Phase 2 scope items. CMS CMPs up to $300/day/bed for non-compliance.",
   "when": ""
